{"tid":379577,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"推廣一下「無限格鬥」比賽","createTime":"2017-08-29T12:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:34:40.000Z","uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d10e3bb5135c965d4a3146b8bf802e6f8d1ee6f7","tid":379577,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"熟悉格鬥GAME一定聽過MUGEN呢個格鬥GAME模擬器<br />\n自己設計角色AI, 將歷代各個格鬥遊戲角色導入, 黎一場大亂鬥<br />\n雖然香港好似唔興呢隻GAME, 但日本卻因此衍生大量次文化<br />\n特別係各式各樣既AI比試<br />\n<br />\n而家我就推介其中三款,  兩款正經, 一款搞笑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm2066576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm2066576&d=eBNIGaalEJNlpssonV7bPsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=533a0e5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm2066576</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">作品團隊對抗戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係第一個日本網民舉辦既大型比賽, 參戰角色大多係傳統格鬥GAME角色<br />\n包括街霸、拳皇、JOJO、GG、侍魂、龍珠等等, 仲有日本再創作既東方系列角色<br />\n到左之後侍魂 VS JOJO更係經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm7995384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm7995384&d=eBNIGaalEJNlpssonV7bPsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=68b8e886\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm7995384</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">主角 VS BOSS 隨機車輪戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另一個有名既比賽, 將各系列主角與BOSS分成兩隊, 隨機抽選打車輪戰<br />\n每連勝一場就減300點HP上限, 直到HP100為止<br />\n雖然話係隨機, 但有時會有各種巧合, 令兩大同作品角色PK而創造經典<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 呢個系列仲有大量FF11二次創作角色及Rider成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm5382291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm5382291&d=eBNIGaalEJNlpssonV7bPsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=0bb2a1a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm5382291</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">9條之人系列  - 先攻擊就會死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n9條之人成名作, 之後仲設計各種荒誕離奇既規則比賽<br />\n有固定班底, 笑料十足,  而且時間短, 各位得閒可以一睇<br />\n呢個系列響YOUTUBE可以搵到<br />\n<br />\n有冇人睇過呢類片, 得閒輕鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附送圖片：怒加運送企業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog-imgs-34.fc2.com/f/r/e/frey01/IMG_000161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-34.fc2.com%2Ff%2Fr%2Fe%2Ffrey01%2FIMG_000161.jpg&h=aca10c00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe04a144b81681576461ddaa4fd888b454b09d3","tid":379577,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"連埋彈幕更精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}